1. Sada je vreme kada trave *proklijavaju* iz zemlje. (Now is the time when the *grasses* are *sprouting* from the ground.)
2. Moramo da *pokosimo* sve trave koje su narasle oko kuće. (We need to *mow* all the *grasses* that have grown around the house.)
3. Ove godine je rodila mnogo trave, ali nije bila dovoljno kvalitetna. (This year she harvested a lot of *grass*, but it wasn't of good enough quality.)
4. Miris sveže pokošene trave je jedan od najlepših mirisa leta. (The scent of freshly mowed *grass* is one of the nicest smells of summer.)
5. Na livadi su bile raznobojne trave koje su se savršeno uklopile u okolinu. (There were colorful *grasses* on the meadow that blended perfectly with the surroundings.)
6. Našao sam divlju ružu koja je rasla među trave. (I found a wild rose that was growing among the *grasses*.)
7. Naša stoka se hrani raznim vrstama trave koju beremo po obližnjim pašnjacima. (Our livestock feeds on various types of *grass* that we gather from nearby pastures.)
8. Lepota planine se ogleda u zelenim padinama obraslim trave. (The beauty of the mountain is reflected in the green slopes covered with *grass*.)
9. Trave su bile natopljene kišom, pa smo morali da odložimo košenje za sledeći dan. (The *grasses* were soaked with rain, so we had to postpone mowing for the next day.)
10. Kada god prolazim pored ovog polja, osećam miris trave koji me vraća u detinjstvo. (Whenever I pass by this field, I smell the scent of *grass* that takes me back to my childhood.)